data.description: Open House  Sat Feb 24 from 1-3 pm. Welcome to this well-maintained home. When entering the home you'll be greeted by the large living room. Just down the hall you will enter into the open concept kitchen with all stainless steel appliances, island, and pantry. The recessed lighting make it bright and cozy. The great room features gas fireplace and cathedral ceilings. The upstairs has four spacious bedrooms. The owner suite with cathedral ceilings, and whirlpool tub in private bath and walk in closet. The lower level has two spacious rec rooms and storage area or you could finish the full bath which the previous owner started. Enjoy your summer evenings on the paver patio with a pergola for some shade. This incredible home is conveniently located, close to restaurants, shopping.
